{"tid":400113,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"(鬥慘大會) 分享下你份工有幾辛苦","createTime":"2017-09-14T13:52:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-14T15:59:19.000Z","uid":118314,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"78d94401aeeb96b37ce8eababcf634a922add771","tid":400113,"uid":118314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T13:52:35.000Z","msg":"日撚日都見到有人話分享份工有幾hea，時間唔知點過，我心諗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小弟分享先，我係做廣告agency <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最近開始覺得有得OT係一種福氣，咁代表你仲有時間可以慢慢做<br />\n最慘係O都O唔撚到T，個客點都要你放工前(佢放工)死比佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n番工唔係比你學野，你跟唔上就只有收皮，每日都係度爆發小宇宙 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n番咗年幾從來冇試過有任何一刻係手頭上冇野做<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n放工攰到會搭錯車、打機水平下降、同人message仲會係咁打錯字 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外奉勸各位想入行嘅朋友，如果你係抱住「我覺得自己幾有創意，好擅長諗idea，應該勝任到呢行」，你千其唔好入 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc9e9e34a84a9f5c11e330fc560f6845edb55b25","tid":400113,"uid":70684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T14:00:29.000Z","msg":"Big4"},{"pid":"665f4158c36b8129d1f29cacaad40e7b8eeb1840","tid":400113,"uid":21861,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T14:26:39.000Z","msg":"日日ot到8點..."},{"pid":"044df7366ef789b7fb04a8d13f9e9bbfa62934ac","tid":400113,"uid":82006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T15:59:19.000Z","msg":"返到屋企臨訓前都仲諗緊公司野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}